news.news: Hauser will come off the bench in Sunday's matchup against the Thunder, Justin Turpin of WEEI.com reports.
news.analysis: With Jaylen Brown (shoulder) returning from a two-game absence, Hauser will slide back to the bench. Over his last five outings (four starts), the 27-year-old has averaged 8.0 points, 2.0 rebounds and 1.6 assists across 20.8 minutes per contest.

news.headline: Joining starting five
news.news: Hauser contributed 15 points (5-11 FG, 5-11 3Pt), three rebounds and two assists across 27 minutes during Thursday's 118-115 win over Minnesota.
